{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SHELF/vellum_simplecloth", "parent": "vellum"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Simple Cloth"], "extent": [49, 66]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Configures SOP-based vellum cloth from geometry and collider."], "extent": [66, 136]}, {"type": "video_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "video", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [136, 144], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"src": "/videos/vellumsimplecloth.mp4"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [185, 200], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool lets you pick a piece of geometry and configure it as vellum cloth.  Rather than building a DOP network, it uses the SOP-level tools to build a simple network to work with the cloth."], "extent": [200, 395]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Simple Cloth"], "extent": [395, 432], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry object to solve as cloth at the SOP level."], "extent": [432, 507]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SHELF/vellum_simplecloth", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SHELF/vellum_simplecloth"}, {"type": "ui", "text": ["Simple Cloth"]}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Simple FX"]}, " tab."], "extent": [507, 603]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry object to use as a collider, if any. This should be a polygonal object.  To collide with volumes or heightfields, use the DOP-based setup."], "extent": [603, 773]}], "container": true}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For specific parameter information, see the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints", "type": "link", "text": ["Vellum Constraints"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vellumsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Vellum Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vellumsolver"}, " help."], "extent": [773, 914]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Working with Simple Cloth"], "extent": [914, 946], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["You can change the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Thickness"]}, " and ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Mass"]}, " of the cloth on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints", "type": "link", "text": ["Vellum Constraints"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints"}, " node. This allows you to set these parameters per piece of cloth."], "extent": [946, 1130]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["The ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Drag"]}, " constraints are useful when animating flags or other objects that are affected by wind."], "extent": [1130, 1234]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["The ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Pin to Animation"]}, " parameters on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints", "type": "link", "text": ["Vellum Constraints"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vellumconstraints"}, " node allow you to directly select points in the viewport to pin using the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "BUTTONS/reselect", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/BUTTONS/reselect"}, " reselect button."], "extent": [1234, 1443], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Choosing ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Stopped"]}, " as the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Pin Type"]}, " sets a ", {"type": "code", "text": ["stopped"]}, " attribute to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["1"]}, " to make the point a hard constraint. This will act like a ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Permanent"]}, " constraint that isn\u2019t affected by forces. However, you can restore dynamics if you choose to move the pin later by resetting the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["stopped"]}, " attribute to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["0"]}, ". This can be done using a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/popawaken", "type": "link", "text": ["POP Awaken"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popawaken"}, "."], "extent": [1443, 1814]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [1814, 1824], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Choosing ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Permanent"]}, " won\u2019t allow you to release the constraint later."], "extent": [1824, 1909]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["Setting a lower ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Compression Stiffness"]}, " allows the cloth to collapse and regain its fluidity. This usually has to be increased for higher resolution cloth so that it doesn\u2019t look too much like silk. "], "extent": [1909, 2116]}], "container": true}]}], "title": ["Simple Cloth"], "summary": ["Configures SOP-based vellum cloth from geometry and collider."]}